@page "/support"

@* Header Image *@
<div class="d-flex justify-center mt-8 page-container">
    <MudImage Src="images/Support.png" Alt="Support Page Image" Class="responsive-img" Style="max-width: 300px; width: 70%;" />
</div>

@* Centered text display *@
<div class="d-flex justify-center mt-8 page-container">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="content-centered">
        ScreenGrab has been a blast to build and maintain, but it does cost time and money. <br /><br />
        There are multiple ways that you can support the development of ScreenGrab: <br />
        - Contribute to the codebase by submitting pull requests on GitHub. <br />
        - Email screengrab.dev@outlook.com with bug reports, feature suggestions, or improvements. <br />
        - Spread the word about ScreenGrab to your colleagues and friends. <br />
        - Donate to support ongoing development and maintenance.
    </MudText>
</div>

@* Clickable donation image *@
<div class="d-flex justify-center mt-8 mb-8 page-container">
    <MudLink Href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/SKWX5HGW44MAY" Underline="Underline.None" Target="_blank">
        <MudImage Src="images/Donate.png" Alt="Donate to ScreenGrab" Class="responsive-img" Style="max-width: 400px; width: 90%;" />
    </MudLink>
</div>

